---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "../../components/shared/Container.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Refund Policy — Flores Nexus Group LLC"
  description="Refund Policy for Flores Nexus Group LLC. Understanding setup fees, monthly fees, and refund scenarios."
  lang="en"
>
  <main class="pt-24 pb-20">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

        <!-- Attorney notice -->
        <p class="text-xs text-heading-3 italic mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          This document is provided for informational purposes. Flores Nexus Group LLC recommends consulting a licensed Florida attorney before relying on these terms for legal decisions.
        </p>

        <!-- Page header -->
        <div class="mb-10">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-heading-1 mb-2">Refund Policy</h1>
          <p class="text-heading-3 text-sm">Flores Nexus Group LLC — Last updated: June 2026</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-0">

          <!-- Overview -->
          <div class="py-6 border-t border-box-border">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading-1 mb-3">Overview</h2>
            <div class="text-sm text-heading-2 leading-relaxed space-y-3">
              <p>Flores Nexus Group LLC provides service-based work. Setup fees cover design, configuration, and launch work that begins after payment and complete onboarding information are received ("production"). Monthly fees cover active hosting, management, and plan-included services for each billing period.</p>
              <p class="font-medium text-heading-1">Key rule: If you cancel before production starts, you receive a full refund of amounts paid, minus the non-refundable payment-processing fees charged by our payment processor (Stripe).</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Refund Scenarios -->
          <div class="py-6 border-t border-box-border">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading-1 mb-6">Refund Scenarios</h2>

            <div class="space-y-4">

              <div class="rounded-xl border border-box-border bg-box-bg p-5">
                <p class="font-semibold text-heading-1 text-sm mb-2">Cancellation before production starts</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-heading-2 leading-relaxed">Full refund of amounts paid, minus non-refundable payment-processing fees.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="rounded-xl border border-box-border bg-box-bg p-5">
                <p class="font-semibold text-heading-1 text-sm mb-2">Client pays but does not provide the information needed to start</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-heading-2 leading-relaxed">Production has not started; the "before production" rule above applies until production begins.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="rounded-xl border border-box-border bg-box-bg p-5">
                <p class="font-semibold text-heading-1 text-sm mb-2">Production already started</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-heading-2 leading-relaxed">Setup fee is non-refundable.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="rounded-xl border border-box-border bg-box-bg p-5">
                <p class="font-semibold text-heading-1 text-sm mb-2">Preview delivered — client cancels</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-heading-2 leading-relaxed">Setup fee is non-refundable. Monthly subscription cancellation follows the billing rule below.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="rounded-xl border border-box-border bg-box-bg p-5">
                <p class="font-semibold text-heading-1 text-sm mb-2">Monthly subscription already charged</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-heading-2 leading-relaxed">Non-refundable for billing periods already started. Canceling stops future charges; service remains active until the end of the paid period unless terminated for a policy violation.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="rounded-xl border border-box-border bg-box-bg p-5">
                <p class="font-semibold text-heading-1 text-sm mb-2">Annual plans</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-heading-2 leading-relaxed">You have a 30-day window from purchase to request a refund of unused full months, minus payment-processing fees. After 30 days, the annual term continues and remaining months are non-refundable.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="rounded-xl border border-box-border bg-box-bg p-5">
                <p class="font-semibold text-heading-1 text-sm mb-2">Error caused by Flores Nexus during the initial build</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-heading-2 leading-relaxed">Corrected at no additional cost within the reasonable scope of the purchased plan.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="rounded-xl border border-box-border bg-box-bg p-5">
                <p class="font-semibold text-heading-1 text-sm mb-2">Add-ons, change requests, and premium domains</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-heading-2 leading-relaxed">Non-refundable once work begins or the resource (e.g., a domain) has been purchased or approved.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="rounded-xl border border-box-border bg-box-bg p-5">
                <p class="font-semibold text-heading-1 text-sm mb-2">Business System custom project</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-heading-2 leading-relaxed">Refunds, milestones, deposits, and cancellation terms are defined in a separate written agreement before work begins.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="rounded-xl border border-box-border bg-box-bg p-5">
                <p class="font-semibold text-heading-1 text-sm mb-2">Unjustified chargeback or payment dispute</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-heading-2 leading-relaxed">Please contact us first; most issues are resolved quickly. An unjustified chargeback may result in suspension or termination of service and forfeiture of any credit.</p>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- How to Request -->
          <div class="py-6 border-t border-box-border">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading-1 mb-3">How to Request a Refund</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-heading-2 leading-relaxed">Email <a href="mailto:info@floresnexus.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@floresnexus.com</a> with your client ID, the plan purchased, and a description of your situation. Approved refunds are issued to the original payment method. We respond within 5 business days.</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </main>
</Layout>
